
 XGngeo - TODO list
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- [DONE] Including a default `romrc' file into XGngeo to be sure to
obtain something nice to handle within a frontend (correct
ROM full names, etc.)
- Joystick key configuration support.
- ROM drivers editing interface (with online synchoniztion
available).
- Quick loading menu for favorite ROMs.
- [DONE] Ability to remove a ROM from the file system through the ROM
list window.
- ROM list generation progress bar.
- Allowing the user to choose the universal BIOS only if the
corresponding files have been found in the BIOS directory.
- [DONE] Ability to customize the background color of
available ROMs in the list.

